Name: "Help!!!"
Desc: A kite the Traveler made under the guidance of Cloud Retainer. It captures Paimon's expression of abject terror, as though she were shouting for help at the top of her little lungs: "It's too high! Someone save Paimon! She's about to faint!"\nThe only question is... Why would one such as Paimon, who can fly, have a fear of heights?
